data.title: Legacy Dental Group
data.text:
Dr. Robert White is a graduate of the University Of Washington School Of Dentistry where he graduated third in his class. Before dental school, Dr. White attended Western Washington University where he graduated Magna Cum Laude with a Bachelor of Science in Anthropology and Biology and a minor in Chemistry.

While at Western Washington University, Dr. White was a four-year letter winner in both varsity football and track and field, receiving numerous awards and recognition for athletics and scholastics.

Dr. White is a Washington State native, born and raised in Woodinville, WA. After college, he married his college sweetheart, Kelsey, and they are the proud parents of two beautiful little girls, Samantha and Frances.
